args: ＂A ninja's true potential is realized\nthrough the act of marriage.＂\n- A Hinomoto Guide for Beginning Ninjas.
Wow, this is some revolutionary stuff!\nBuuuuut...
I bet it would be hard to actually DO\nthis, though... Hmm...
What has you so fascinated, Aoi?
The guide I've been getting by carrier\npigeon is talking about an AMAZING\nnew category of ninja techniques!
They're called ＂ninja bride＂ skills,\nand they're taking our world by storm!
Yep! Basically, you fight like a bride\nwould while wearing a wedding dress.
Wedding dresses are sacred in Hinomoto,\nand believed to purify the body of evil.
So these skills involve using a dress\nto purify yourself and unleash your\ninner power.
And all of that comes from merely\nwearing a wedding dress?

You know it, sister! Heck, plenty of
miracles in Hinomoto have been brought
about by the power of love and the
resolve to stay with someone for life.
So that means all this stuff must have an\neffect. ...Probably. I don't ACTUALLY know,\nbut I'm pretty sure it works.
It sounds like these wedding dresses\nof Hinomoto are no ordinary garments.
Still, I'm never gonna know if this stuff\nactually works or not because I don't\nown a wedding dress. Boo!
Normally, I'd just throw in the towel at\nthis point and move on to something else.\nBut not this time!
See, 'cause I'll be a lot more help to the\nprince if I can master these new skills.
After he accepted me despite all my\nweirdness, chipping in more around\nhere is the least I can do.
So I don't want to give up\nat the first hurdle!
If I might ask, is the design for the dress \nyou want in that guide of yours?
Yep! They put in a complete set of\ninstructions for folks who want to\ntry making their own dress.
Then I have everything I need.
Wait, you're gonna MAKE me one?!
How could I refuse after seeing your\ndevotion to {player_name}?
Aw, thanks, Cleo! You're the BEST!
I can't believe I'm wearing a real wedding\ndress right now. You're AMAZING, Cleo!
Your joy in receiving it has made all\nof my effort worth it. Good luck.
I won't let you down! I'm gonna train real\nhard and keep my master safe!
Heya, Aoi! I hear you're gonna be trying\nout some crazy new ninja skills?
So, like, what kind of ninja stuff can you\neven DO in a wedding dress?
Yeah, do ya attack like yer cuttin' a cake\nor somethin'?
Well, I think cake-cutting's an Alberian\ntradition. But here, let me check the\nguide for an example...
Ah, here's an interesting ninja bride skill.\n＂Fine Cutlery＂!\nHiiiiyayayaya!
Ow! Hey, watch where you're\nswingin' that thing, kid!
Aaagh! You're going to shred our clothes!
Please stop! I don't want to have to\nrepair everyone's torn garments!
Nooo! I need my clothes! They're the only\nthing that keeps me from being naked!
I suppose it does make fine cuts...\nWait, this is no time for pondering the\nname! Stop attacking us, Aoi!
You are supposed to PROTECT the prince,\nnot dice him up and serve him to guests!
Ack! Okay, I'm stopping, I'm stopping!
Holy crow, man. I thought I was\ngonna be sliced to ribbons there.

Hmm... According to my guide,
that technique is supposed to be for
creating an elegant atmosphere,
not hurting people.
Perhaps it would be better suited to\nmore relevant circumstances.
Ooooh! So I just used it at the wrong time!\nHee hee! Oh man, what a dope.
A ＂dope＂? Ya just tried to murder us!
Yes, but she DIDN'T murder anyone,\nwhich is all that really matters.
And while it certainly could have gone\nbetter, isn't that what training is for?
Yep! In the future, I'll use my skills\nproperly AND learn lots of new ones!
Good luck, Aoi. We're counting on you!
I won't let you down! I'm gonna become\nthe strongest ninja bride in the land!
